问题描述
########################
health status index            uuid                   pri rep docs.count docs.deleted store.size pri.store.size
yellow open   kplat-2023.10.31 MC9Yp47yTwW1QVZN4tuPJQ   1   1      11680            0      1.6mb          1.6mb

########################
solution
########################

add configuration option  to  settings

"index" : {
     "number_of_replicas" : 0
 }

